verbose_text: As shown in Fig. XREF_FIG b, Cells were treated with docetaxel (100 ng/ml) for 0, 2, 4, 8, 12 h, and western blot assay results showed that the expression of p-Bcl-2 and Beclin1 protein expression increased in a time dependent manner after docetaxel treatment compared with that in the control group.
